{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/apa-yang-ditawarkan-microsoft-dengan-joystick-xbox-untuk-difabel-xbox-adaptive-controller/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Apa yang Ditawarkan Microsoft dengan Joystick Xbox untuk Difabel “Xbox Adaptive Controller” ?","content":"<p><em>Video game</em> adalah soal kendali atau kontrol sebuah permainan yang ditayangkan melalui sebuah layar. Sejak <em>video game</em> jadul “Pong” dirilis ke pasaran hingga <em>game</em> modern seperti “God of War”, aspek kendali merupakan sebuah bagian tidak terpisahkan dari permainan <em>video game</em>.</p>\n<p>Papan kendali untuk video game lazim disebut sebagai “<em>Controller</em>” atau “<em>Joystick</em>” sejak dulu. Benda ini juga terus mengalami evolusi demi evolusi untuk memberikan pemain <em>game,</em> rasa kendali penuh atas permainan yang sedang mereka mainkan.</p>\n<p>Dulu di <em>video game</em> <em>arcade</em>, papan kendali ini melekat di mesin<em> game</em> itu sendiri dengan sebuah <em>stick</em> dan deretan tombol. Dengan <em>stick</em> dan tombol itulah pemain mengendalikan jalannya permainan di layar hingga selesai.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48327\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48327\" data-attachment-id=\"48327\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-yang-ditawarkan-microsoft-dengan-joystick-xbox-untuk-difabel-xbox-adaptive-controller/attachment/xbox1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"xbox1Video Game Arcade. (Sumber: ArcadeTimeMachine)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Video Game Arcade. (Sumber: ArcadeTimeMachine)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48327\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox1.jpg\" alt=\"Video Game Arcade. (Sumber: ArcadeTimeMachine)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48327\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Video Game Arcade. (Sumber: ArcadeTimeMachine)</p></div></p>\n<p>Masuk ke generasi <em>home console, joystick</em> mulai mengalami evolusi besar. Benda itu tidak lagi melekat di mesin namun disambungkan dengan kabel. Perubahan ini memberikan rasa nyaman buat pemain <em>game console</em> karena mereka tidak perlu berada terlalu dekat dengan mesin <em>game</em> dan punya kebebasan bergerak jika dibandingkan <em>joystick</em> di mesin video <em>game arcade</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48328\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48328\" data-attachment-id=\"48328\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-yang-ditawarkan-microsoft-dengan-joystick-xbox-untuk-difabel-xbox-adaptive-controller/attachment/xbox2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Joystick video game era ‘90an. (Sumber: PicCick)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Joystick video game era ‘90an. (Sumber: PicCick)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48328\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox2.jpg\" alt=\"Joystick video game era ‘90an. (Sumber: PicCick)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48328\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Joystick video game era ‘90an. (Sumber: PicCick)</p></div></p>\n<p>Evolusi di bagian <em>joystick console</em> ini bahkan memungkinkan sebuah <em>joystick</em> tidak lagi mengandalkan kabel penghubung karena sudah mengadopsi teknologi gelombang radio atau <em>wireless</em> dan bahkan memiliki <em>gyroscope</em> alias kemampuan sensorik pergerakan; sehingga <em>gamers</em> tidak hanya mengandalkan sentuhan ataupun tekanan di tombol <em>joystick</em> namun juga pergerakan <em>joystick</em> itu sendiri secara total (atas-bawah-kiri-kanan-menyamping-360 derajat pergerakan).</p>\n<p>Saat ini pengendalian dalam<em> game</em> bahkan sudah dapat melibatkan pergerakan tubuh manusia itu sendiri lewat kamera sensorik yang menangkap citra serta pergerakan <em>gamers</em> dan mengaplikasikannya sebagai kendali dalam<em> game</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48329\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48329\" data-attachment-id=\"48329\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-yang-ditawarkan-microsoft-dengan-joystick-xbox-untuk-difabel-xbox-adaptive-controller/attachment/xbox3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"xbox3\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kendali video game dengan motion sensor dari kamera khusus. (Sumber: VideogamesBlogger)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48329\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48329\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kendali video game dengan motion sensor dari kamera khusus. (Sumber: VideogamesBlogger)</p></div></p>\n<p>Semua mekanisme dan kenyamanan <em>joystick video game console</em> itu mengakomodasi para pemain <em>video game</em> ‘biasa/normal’ yang memiliki kelengkapan motorik. Panca indera yang komplit. Karena memang <em>video game</em> biasanya ditujukan untuk orang yang demikian. Tapi bermain <em>game</em> juga bukan monopoli kelompok manusia yang memiliki kelengkapan maupun panca indera yang komplit. Ada pula manusia kelompok difabel; yaitu kelompok yang tidak memiliki kelengkapan ataupun punya keterbatasan motorik. Bagaimana mengakomodasi mereka agar dapat menikmati<em> video game</em> seperti manusia lain?</p>\n<p>Microsoft melihat kondisi ini dan menciptakan <strong>“Xbox Adaptive Controller </strong>atau <strong>XAC”</strong>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48335\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48335\" data-attachment-id=\"48335\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-yang-ditawarkan-microsoft-dengan-joystick-xbox-untuk-difabel-xbox-adaptive-controller/attachment/xbox9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"xbox9\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber gambar: Xbox&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48335\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48335\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber gambar: Xbox</p></div></p>\n<p>Sesuai dengan namanya, <em>joystick</em> XAC dari Microsoft ini memiliki kemampuan beradaptasi untuk menyesuaikan dengan kebutuhan <em>gamer</em> yang menggunakannya. Adaptasi itu diwakili dari desain<em> joystick</em>: XAC di desain dengan pemikiran ‘<em>different folks different needs</em>’ alias beda orang beda kebutuhan.</p>\n<p>XAC memiliki dua tombol besar di tengah-tengah dengan berbagai slot input untuk tambahan peripheral yang sesuai kebutuhan gamer yang menggunakan XAC. Ada 19 input jack 3.5mm yang dapat dipasang <em>add-ons</em> apa saja yang mendukung kendali untuk bermain <em>game.</em> Semuanya format “<em>industrial standard”</em> sehingga bersifat universal. Contoh: jika tidak bisa menggunakan d-pad maka <em>gamer</em> bisa mengganti fungsi d-pad dengan benda lain yang menawarkan kinerja yang sama melalui <em>add-on</em>. Tersedia pula slot USB untuk koneksi tambahan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48334\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48334\" data-attachment-id=\"48334\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-yang-ditawarkan-microsoft-dengan-joystick-xbox-untuk-difabel-xbox-adaptive-controller/attachment/xbox8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"xbox8\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Slot koneksi yang tersedia. (Sumber: PCGamer)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48334\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48334\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Slot koneksi yang tersedia. (Sumber: PCGamer)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9fcK19CAjWM\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>XAC berjalan dengan mengemulasikan <em>joystick</em> Xbox standar Microsoft sehingga benda ini akan berjalan baik di Xbox One maupun Windows PC. Gamer difabel dapat bermain <em>game</em> dengan memanfaatkan fitur-fitur yang ada di XAC untuk “mengatasi kerepotan” disabilitas yang dia miliki saat bermain <em>game</em> menggunakan<em> joystick</em> biasa selama ini. Seperti misalnya menggunakan <em>QuadStick</em> yang dapat dioperasikan dengan mulut. Dua tombol besar di XAC bersifat <em>‘fully programable’</em> yang dapat disetel sesuai kebutuhan <em>gamer</em>. Dan karena <em>form factor</em> alias bentuknya yang rata, XAC dapat diletakkan di atas lantai dan <em>gamer</em> bahkan bisa menggunakan kaki mereka di <em>joystick</em> canggih ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48330\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48330\" data-attachment-id=\"48330\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-yang-ditawarkan-microsoft-dengan-joystick-xbox-untuk-difabel-xbox-adaptive-controller/attachment/xbox4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"xbox4\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Bermain game balap dengan QuadStick. (Sumber: YouTube)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48330\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48330\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bermain game balap dengan QuadStick. (Sumber: YouTube)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wEKIAHrugZ4\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mekanisme Xbox Adaptive Controller</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48331\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48331\" data-attachment-id=\"48331\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-yang-ditawarkan-microsoft-dengan-joystick-xbox-untuk-difabel-xbox-adaptive-controller/attachment/xbox5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"xbox5\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Skenario pemanfaatan XAC untuk gamer dengan disabilitas. (Sumber: DigitalTrends)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48331\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48331\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Skenario pemanfaatan XAC untuk gamer dengan disabilitas. (Sumber: DigitalTrends)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48332\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48332\" data-attachment-id=\"48332\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-yang-ditawarkan-microsoft-dengan-joystick-xbox-untuk-difabel-xbox-adaptive-controller/attachment/xbox6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"xbox6\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Skenario lain pemanfaatan XAC untuk gamer dengan disabilitas motorik. (Sumber: SkyNews)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48332\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48332\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Skenario lain pemanfaatan XAC untuk gamer dengan disabilitas motorik. (Sumber: SkyNews)</p></div></p>\n<p>Harga retail Xbox Adaptive<em> Controller</em> yang US$99 itu memang sedikit lebih mahal ketimbang <em>joystick</em> Xbox standar. Belum lagi harga <em>add-ons</em> tambahan yang, syukurnya, bisa dibeli sesuai kebutuhan alias dijual terpisah (dan bahkan tidak perlu berasal dari Microsoft sendiri karena XAC akan menerima peripheral pabrikan lain selama bendanya <em>‘industrial standard</em>’). Tapi dengan apa yang ditawarkan oleh benda ini untuk kenyamanan bermain kelompok<em> gamers</em> difabel, rasanya harga yang ada bisa di justifikasi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48333\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48333\" data-attachment-id=\"48333\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/apa-yang-ditawarkan-microsoft-dengan-joystick-xbox-untuk-difabel-xbox-adaptive-controller/attachment/xbox7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"xbox7\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Bermain untuk gamer difabel akan semakin menyenangkan. (Sumber: TechSourceInternational)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48333\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/xbox7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48333\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bermain untuk gamer difabel akan semakin menyenangkan. (Sumber: TechSourceInternational)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kini kelompok difabel bisa semakin menikmati permainan <em>video game t</em>anpa merasakan keribetan beradaptasi dengan<em> joystick</em> ‘biasa’ yang tidak sesuai kondisi tubuh mereka. Dan saya pribadi penasaran gimana bermain dengan <em>joystick</em> ini. Saya membayangkan bermain<em> game</em> seperti Tekken dengan menggunakan kaki di <em>joystick</em> ini akan melelahkan tapi kayakya bakal seru banget. Menurut kamu?</p>\n<p>Psst, Xbox Adaptive Controller atau XAC sudah dipamerkan di E3 2018.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"98b74501-e798-553f-9471-11666bf0bfc0"}}}